The game is being rigged. Terrible matchmaking. You will face the same stuff every time until you change your team to something else. And i will never forget the time where you could not even do anything but watch your pokemon go down while your charge move and switch button disappear. Most sickening times. The game is so broken. You have to restart the app every few battles to avoid all the bugs and lag. And hiding elo points in the future is throwing an even thicker curtain over the players eyes. How does this game design make any sense? It is so disgusting the delays after charge moves calculating every win con for the game to be as rigged as possible.
